OL,3,CUrgent investigation ordered into
OL,4,CHeathrow power outage, says Ed Miliband
OL,6,FAn urgent investigation has been
OL,7,Fordered into the power outage that
OL,8,Fshut Heathrow Airport, the Energy
OL,9,FSecretary has announced.
OL,11,FEd Miliband has told the National
OL,12,FEnergy System Operator to "urgently
OL,13,Finvestigate" the substation fire that
OL,14,Fcaused travel chaos on Friday.
OL,16,FHe is working with Ofgem and using
OL,17,Fpowers under the Energy Act to
OL,18,Fformally launch the grid operator's
OL,19,Finvestigation.
