OL,3,CUrgent investigation ordered into
OL,4,CHeathrow power outage, says Ed Miliband
OL,6,F"We are determined to properly
OL,7,Funderstand what happened and what
OL,8,Flessons need to be learned," Mr
OL,9,FMiliband said.
OL,11,F"That is why, working with Ofgem, I
OL,12,Fhave today commissioned the National
OL,13,FEnergy System Operator to carry out an
OL,14,Finvestigation into this specific
OL,15,Fincident and to understand any wider
OL,16,Flessons to be learned on energy
OL,17,Fresilience for critical national
OL,18,Finfrastructure, both now and in the
OL,19,Ffuture.
