OL,3,CUrgent investigation ordered into
OL,4,CHeathrow power outage, says Ed Miliband
OL,6,F"The Government is determined to do
OL,7,Feverything it can to prevent a repeat
OL,8,Fof what happened at Heathrow."
OL,10,FMeanwhile, an internal review of the
OL,11,Fairport's crisis management plans and
OL,12,Fits response to the power outage will
OL,13,Fbe undertaken by former transport
OL,14,Fsecretary Ruth Kelly, who is an
OL,15,Findependent member of Heathrow's board.
OL,17,FHeathrow chairman Lord Paul Deighton
OL,18,Fsaid: "Closing the airport yesterday
OL,19,Fhad significant impacts for our
OL,20,Fpassengers, our customers, our
OL,21,Fcolleagues and the country.
