OL,3,CUrgent investigation ordered into
OL,4,CHeathrow power outage, says Ed Miliband
OL,6,F"Heathrow regrets the disruption this
OL,7,Fcaused. We hope that all those
OL,8,Faffected understand that the decision
OL,9,Fwas made in order to prioritise the
OL,10,Fsafety of our passengers and
OL,11,Fcolleagues.
OL,13,F"We are committed to finding any
OL,14,Fpotential learnings from this
OL,15,Funprecedented incident.
OL,17,F"To fully understand what happened, I
OL,18,Fhave asked Ruth Kelly, former
OL,19,Fsecretary of state for transport and
OL,20,Fan independent member of Heathrow's
OL,21,FBoard, to undertake a review.
