OL,3,CUrgent investigation ordered into
OL,4,CHeathrow power outage, says Ed Miliband
OL,6,F"The Kelly Review will analyse all of
OL,7,Fthe relevant material concerning the
OL,8,Frobustness and execution of Heathrow's
OL,9,Fcrisis management plans, the airport's
OL,10,Fresponse during the incident and how
OL,11,Fthe airport recovered the operation
OL,12,Fwith the objective of identifying any
OL,13,Fimprovements that could be made to our
OL,14,Ffuture resilience."
OL,16,FFlights resumed at the west London
OL,17,Fairport on Friday evening and
OL,18,Frestrictions on overnight flights were
OL,19,Ftemporarily lifted after hours of
OL,20,Fclosure.
